          "description": "\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\n\nI\u2019m so grateful to Canal Dental Group for taking such great care of my emergency tooth situation. A special thank you to Dr. Zhu for the excellent care during my emergency visit \u2014 professional, gentle, and very reassuring throughout a stressful experience.\n\nI\u2019d also like to thank dental hygienist Yuki, who took great care of me during my second visit for my teeth cleaning. She was incredibly kind, gentle, and thorough, and made the whole experience very comfortable.\n\nThe front desk team was also so warm, attentive, and welcoming. From scheduling my appointments to making sure everything went smoothly, they made me feel cared for from the moment I walked in.\n\nThe entire team at Canal Dental Group truly goes above and beyond. I really appreciated how well they took care of me during both visits, and I highly recommend them to anyone looking for exceptional dental care. Thank you all so much!",
