          "description": "I\u2019ve been a patient at Canal Dental Group for several years, and my recent visit was another reminder of why I keep coming back. I had my cleaning done by a young hygienist I hadn't met before, and she was fantastic.\n\nShe took the time to clearly communicate every step of the process before starting and answered all my questions in a way that was very easy to understand. Since I have sensitive teeth, I\u2019m always a bit nervous, but she took special care throughout the procedure and reacted to my signals promptly and patiently.\n\nAs always, the office environment is modern, spotless, and very clean. The entire staff is professional and friendly, and I appreciated the minimal wait time. Highly recommend!",
